{"type": "article", "id": 5734, "title": "夜宿阿尔卑斯山上的缆车", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-30T07:48:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233919lAPOz7yweWhHiEM4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在法国阿尔卑斯山上的缆车里过夜，肯定能带来非一般的体验。日前，短租网站 Airbnb 就推出了这样的服务，他们将挑选幸运的游客，带着 3 名亲友，在滑雪胜地 Courchevel 离地 9000 尺的  SAULIRE 缆车上住一晚。而 Airbnb 也对缆车进行了改头换面，变成了客房，客人当晚还可以享受一顿芝士火锅，一早起来再赶往滑雪场。如若想要赢得这一机会，参与者需在 2 月 26 日之前<a href=\"https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/4596095?cdn_cn=1&amp;locale=en\" target=\"_blank\">向 Airnbnb 提交想去SAULIRE 缆车过夜的原因</a>，等待审核通过。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233917GplzRwCn0btyhXUe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233917hH7enV5XzsCWpZKN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052339175SNbsG981tjFCH7r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233918gyMY1DSRLtEdfNpT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}